Class AppLayer

@Generated(value="org.openapitools.codegen.languages.SpringCodegen", comments="Generator version: 7.13.0") public class AppLayer extends Object implements Serializable
A map layer, but only enough information to draw the layer. For advanced functionality that required access to attributes the LayerDetails should be requested.
